"modifier matrix" is a list of to-hit/area fire modifiers as follows:
infantry moved, infantry dug in, infantry stationary,
gun moved, gun dug in, gun stationary,
vehicle moved, vehicle stationary, recce vehicle moved, recce vehicle stationary
-->
